Installation EMU 0404 PCI and other sound card on Linux

1 search google kxstudio project (today https://kx.studio/Repositories )
2 select repositories and install repositories (follow instructions)
3 now run apt-get update ( to update repositories)
4 install apt-get install -y alsa-firmware-loaders alsa-firmware
5 restart system
6 EMU 0404 PUMP YOUR SPEAKER

Thanks to Linux Italia group,Paolo S. for solution and Kxstudio project to pump my emu 0404 

Saltui Ale
